# Sentence Types
S -> NP.Nom VP
S -> NP.Acc VP
S -> NP.Nom NP.Pred
S -> VP.Pass
S -> NP.Nom ADJ.Pred
S -> VP PUNCT
S -> VP.Ques
VP -> VP.Imp
S -> NP.Pred
S -> ADJ.Pred PUNCT

VP -> Verb
ADJP -> ADJ
ADJP -> ADV ADJ
NP -> Noun

# Punctuation
Ques -> VP.Ques PUNCT.Ques
Decl -> S PUNCT

"git": "Verb.Nom.Dat" 
S -> NP.Nom NP.Dat git

# Verbal Predicate
VP -> NP.Bare VP
VP -> NP.Nom VP
VP -> NP.Acc VP
VP -> NP.Dat VP
VP -> NP.Loc VP
VP -> NP.Abl VP
VP -> NP.Ins VP
VP -> POSTP VP
VP -> ADV VP

# Verbal Predicate (Questions)
S -> VP QuesP
S -> QuesP VP

# Nominal Predicate
NP.Pred -> NP.Bare NP.Pred
NP.Pred -> NP.Acc NP.Pred
NP.Pred -> NP.Dat NP.Pred
NP.Pred -> NP.Loc NP.Pred
NP.Pred -> NP.Abl NP.Pred
NP.Pred -> NP.Ins NP.Pred
NP.Pred -> NP.Gen NP.Pred
NP.Pred -> ADJ NP.Pred
# Look at ADV to NP.Mod
NP -> N.Gen N.Poss

# (Bare) Possesive Constructions
NP.Acc -> NP.Bare NP.Acc
NP.Dat -> NP.Bare NP.Dat
NP.Loc -> NP.Bare NP.Loc
NP.Abl -> NP.Bare NP.Abl
NP.Ins -> NP.Bare NP.Ins

# Genitive Possesive Constructions
NP.Nom -> NP.Nom NP.Poss.Bare
NP.Acc -> NP.Gen NP.Poss.Acc
NP.Dat -> NP.Gen NP.Poss.Dat
NP.Loc -> NP.Gen NP.Poss.Loc
NP.Abl -> NP.Gen NP.Poss.Abl
NP.Ins -> NP.Gen NP.Poss.Ins
NP.Bare -> NP.Gen NP.Poss.Bare

NP.Poss.Acc -> ADJ NP.Poss.Acc
NP.Poss.Dat -> ADJ NP.Poss.Dat
NP.Poss.Loc -> ADJ NP.Poss.Loc
NP.Poss.Abl -> ADJ NP.Poss.Abl
NP.Poss.Ins -> ADJ NP.Poss.Ins
NP.Poss.Bare -> ADJ NP.Poss.Bare
NP.Poss.Pred -> ADJ NP.Poss.Pred

NP.Pred -> NP.Gen NP.Poss.Pred

# Adjectives
NP.Acc -> ADJ NP.Acc
NP.Dat -> ADJ NP.Dat
NP.Loc -> ADJ NP.Loc
NP.Abl -> ADJ NP.Abl
NP.Bare -> ADJ NP.Bare
NP.Ins -> ADJ NP.Ins

NP.Acc -> NP.Rel NP.Acc
NP.Dat -> NP.Rel NP.Dat
NP.Loc -> NP.Rel NP.Loc
NP.Abl -> NP.Rel NP.Abl
NP.Bare -> NP.Rel NP.Bare
NP.Ins -> NP.Rel NP.Ins

ADJ -> ADV ADJ

# Adjectival Predicate
ADJ.Pred -> NP.Bare ADJ.Pred
ADJ.Pred -> NP.Bare ADJ.Pred
ADJ.Pred -> NP.Nom ADJ.Pred
ADJ.Pred -> NP.Acc ADJ.Pred
ADJ.Pred -> NP.Dat ADJ.Pred
ADJ.Pred -> NP.Loc ADJ.Pred
ADJ.Pred -> NP.Abl ADJ.Pred
ADJ.Pred -> NP.Ins ADJ.Pred
ADJ.Pred -> ADV ADJ.Pred
# Look at ADV to NP.Mod
NP -> N.Gen N.Poss

# Coordination
NP.Acc -> NP.Acc x1
x1 -> CONJ NP.Acc
NP.Dat -> NP.Dat CONJ NP.Dat
NP.Loc -> NP.Loc CONJ NP.Loc
NP.Abl -> NP.Abl CONJ NP.Abl
NP.Ins -> NP.Ins CONJ NP.Ins

# Determiners
NP.Bare -> Det NP.Bare
NP.Acc -> Det NP.Acc
NP.Dat -> Det NP.Dat
NP.Loc -> Det NP.Loc
NP.Abl -> Det NP.Abl
NP.Ins -> Det NP.Ins

# Questions
QuesP -> Ques NP.Bare
QuesP -> ADJP QuesP
VP -> VP QuesP

#Post Positions
POSTP -> NP Postp
POSTP -> NP.Acc POSTP
POSTP -> NP.Dat POSTP
POSTP -> NP.Loc POSTP
POSTP -> NP.Abl POSTP
POSTP -> NP.Ins POSTP

Sentences

- ADV NP.Dat Det Noun.Bare Verb (Dün arkadaşıma bir hediye aldım.) [x]

- [ADJ NP.Acc] NP.Ins Verb (Tarihi romanları keyifle okuyorum) [x]

- NP.Nom NP(Date) NP.Acc POSTP NP.Dat NP.Bare Verb (Ben dün akşam yemeği için anneme yardım ettim.)

- NP.Nom NP.Bare NP.Acc Conj NP.Acc Verb (Destanlar milli kültürümüzü ve tarihimizi anlatır.)

- NP(Date) NP.Abl NP.Nom] ADV ADV ADJ NP.Pred (Yaz meyvelerinden karpuz bence en güzel meyvedir.)

- Det NP.Rel NP.Dat Verb Ques PUNCT.Ques (Bu akşamki toplantıya katılacak mısınız?) 

- Det NP.Gen NP.Dat Det NP(Date) NP.Acc Verb (Bu ağacın altında her gece mehtabı izlerdik.) 

- NP.Nom NP.Dat ADV ADJ Ques NP.Bare Verb PUNCT.Ques (Siz buraya en son ne zaman geldiniz?)

- NP.Gen Num(ADJ) NP.Poss NP.Gen NP.Pred (Anadolu’nun dört yanı medeniyetin beşiğidir. )

- ProperNoun ProperNoun.Poss NP.Gen ADJ ADJ(NP) NP.Pred (Orhun Abideleri Türkçenin ilk yazılı örnekleridir.)

- NP NP.Gen NP.Dat ADV NP.Pred

- ADJ NP.Ins NP.Bare Verb.Imp 
 


 

 
Okul bizim köye epeyce uzaktaydı. 
Yüksek sesle müzik dinleme


